# Title: Use of VSIISExeLauncher.exe
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-06-09
# Level: medium
# Description: The "VSIISExeLauncher.exe" binary part of the Visual Studio/VS Code can be used to execute arbitrary binaries
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1127
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_lolbin_vsiisexelauncher.yml

CommandLine IN ("* -p *", "* -a *") Image="*\\VSIISExeLauncher.exe" OR OriginalFileName="VSIISExeLauncher.exe"